description:
This is a 35 minute workout called '30-Minute Bodyweight Workout' from the channel PS Fit .
The workout falls under Strength/Body weight and Cardio/HIIT.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout and The Endorphin Wave vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.
